   9.external css can be achived by link tag and it can be used for many html codes
   
   10. element selector -- for a single tag
   
        group selector --  for 2 or more tag
		class selector --  it was specified by class
		
		id selector --  it was specified by id
		
		
		11. content -- it consist of text and images
		
		     padding  --  it gives the space for content 
			 margin -- it contains padding and content
			 
			 Border -- it consist of padding and margin it gives outerline for content
			 
			 div{
			 
			 padding : 5px 10px 5px 10px;
			 margin : 5px;
			 border : 10%;
			 
			 
			 }
			 
			 
			 
